Langkah-langkah Install MariaDB di Linux Mint:

1. Buka Terminal

2. Update dan upgrade sistem:
  sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y

3. Install MariaDB:
 sudo apt install mariadb-server -y

4. Cek status service MariaDB:
 sudo systemctl status mariadb

5. Jika belum aktif, jalankan:
   sudo systemctl start mariadb

6. Aktifkan MariaDB saat boot:
   sudo systemctl enable mariadb

7. Akses MariaDB:
   sudo mariadB 

Selesai. MariaDB siap digunakan.

